{"id": "webh_kanban", "modality": "web", "name": "Kanban", "task": {"description": "Build a project board (Kanban) for 'ShipIt' at 1920px wide. A top bar shows the board name, a member-avatars stack, and a 'New task' button. Below, FOUR equal-width columns (Backlog, In Progress, Review, Done) with uniform gutters, each with a column header showing the title and a count badge, and a vertical stack of task cards. Distribute at least 14 task cards across the columns (Backlog 5, In Progress 4, Review 3, Done 2); each card shows a title, a small colored label chip, an assignee avatar, and a due date. Responsive: at 375px the four columns stack into one vertical column in order, each column's cards beneath its header.", "requirements": ["Exactly four columns (Backlog, In Progress, Review, Done) of equal width with uniform gutters between them", "The four column headers share the same top edge and each shows a title plus a count badge", "At least 14 task cards total are distributed across the columns", "Every task card shows a title, a colored label chip, an assignee avatar, and a due date, none clipped", "All cards within a column are equal width and left/right aligned to their column", "No card overlaps another card or column header", "On desktop nothing overflows horizontally (no horizontal scrollbar)", "At 375px the four columns stack vertically in order with each column's cards under its header", "Card label chips share one consistent style across all cards (repetition)", "Column count badges match the number of cards shown in each column"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 6, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 4980, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 2, "rv_total_tokens": 15562}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 6, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 4994, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_